{
  "stem": "26142.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother, Moshe, his wife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had two children-- a girl that was that time, about seven, and an boy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Her name was Chani.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the boy's name was Shloime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was about five or four and a half, five years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had nowhere-- nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He stayed in-- in his house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This happened two weeks-- I-- I would say, August the 2nd.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This must have been in July, the middle of July, that my two brothers' wives and children were away from Torun.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we still stay-- we still stayed in Torun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "On the night of the-- of the Tisha B'av night of the 2 and 3, there was a labor unit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A Jewish labor unit was assigned, but they-- those were not from Torun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Those were Jewish boys from deep in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were-- they were assigned to this-- to this Hungarian brigade that was there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember I went to the s-- to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's u-- it's customary to on a-- on a-- on a fast day, especially on Tisha B'av, fast day, where you fast.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But you talk about the destruction of the-- of the [NON-ENGLISH], of the holy temple that took place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We are now in 1941.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It took place, that time, about 1,920 years ago-- that you say [NON-ENGLISH] and [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was sitting in the- in the-- in the-- synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And somehow, I-- I-- my mood wasn't-- wasn't too-- too good.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And across from the synagogue was a house where there was a-- a couple that the father died not-- not too long before and also the mother.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there were three sisters and-- and-- and one older sister that was married that lived in this house, and two younger sisters and two-- and two boys.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
